dct_description_sm: United States. Defense Mapping Agency. Hydrographic/Topographic Center. Guatemala. Instituto Geografico Militar. In upper left margin: Ciudad de Guatemala - escala 1:15,000. Transverse Mercator projection. Relief shown by 10 meter contour intervals and spot elevation. One map on four sheets. With a glossary. Map information as of 1985.
